	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Dr. James Hansen of GISS is a Liar and a Fraud</h1>

		<div class="entry-meta">
			<a class="author" rel="author" href="http://hennessysview.com/author/bhennessy/">Bill Hennessy</a> / <a class="entry-date" href="http://hennessysview.com/2008/07/23/dr-james-hansen-of-giss-is-a-liar-and-a-fraud/">July 23, 2008</a>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Dr. Hansen purposely and with malice aforethought manipulates actual temperature observations in order to perpetuate a global warming hoax.</p>
<p>If I&#8217;m wrong, he can sue me.Â  But he won&#8217;t, because he&#8217;s a fraud.</p>
